Metafrash:
H metafrash tou kwdika ginetai me ena makefile sto opoio dhmiourgountai
ta object files tou library kai to test program kai ginontai telika link se ena 
teliko executable "test".

Dokimh:
Gia thn dokimh tou kwdika yparxei to script "run_test.sh" to opoio mporei na xrhsimopoihthei
me 3 diaforetika flags to kathena gia diaforetiko input file sto test program. To script 
trexei to test program kai afou teleiwsei elegxei ta .copy kai .copy2 me diff an einai idia 
me to original file kai typwnei to analogo result.